overview: Ann-Margret gave viewers a double dose of movie star glamour in 1975, with a pair of TV specials designed to showcase her musical and comedic talents. Arriving first up in January was this program  "Ann-Margret Olsson" with guest stars The Osmonds and Ike & Tina Turner Turner.  (The follow-up special "Ann-Margret Smith" debuted in November.)
tagline: Ann Margret brings her special kind of glamour to TV!
title: Ann-Margret Olsson
